text: Emphytoecia niveopicta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaie and Germain in 1864. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Emphytoecia niveopicta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1864
title: Emphytoecia niveopicta
